Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.07,0:00:05.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your arms and face this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.07,0:00:05.94,sign_74_2_Raise_your_arms_,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(310,1)}Raise your arms and face this way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:10.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they'd called in backup, \Nbut you're just two kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:13.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Port Mafia short-staffed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.72,0:00:17.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Or is that man, Randou, not very popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:18.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Randou?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:22.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's the name of the man \Nwe're about to go talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:26.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The person that was restraining \Nyou using his special ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:28.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.89,0:00:31.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, old fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:33.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Let's save us both some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:35.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,First, you shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:39.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I'll retaliate by blowing you \Nall the way to the next town over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:43.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll beat the shit \Nout of your remaining men,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:46.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:47.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.07,0:00:52.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you could just trick him to \Nget some information out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:56.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're with the GSS tactical team, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:01:00.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Gerhardt Security Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:04.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Formerly a foreign-funded \Nprivate security firm,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:06.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,but they had their subsidies cut off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:09.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,and now they're a fully-fledged \Nillegal organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:10.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.22,0:01:12.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go easy on you \Njust because you're kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:15.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Try me, old fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:27.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:30.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Sheep, Nakahara Chuuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:35.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,So it was true that you fell \Ninto the Port Mafia's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:41.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea, \Nyou annoying prick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:47.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Were you just standing there watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:52.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I was busy collecting information from \Nthe communicator I swiped off him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:57.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the guy you just beat up\N has some backup arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:03.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You just make more work when you \Ndon't think about what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:13.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:16.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Want to join him in the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:17.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:20.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,That shrimp is the gravity \Nmanipulator Nakahara Chuuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:39.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just call me a shrimp, asshole?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:42.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only fifteen years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:46.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still growing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:22.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the reason for the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:26.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about Arahabaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:31.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to wait for \Nour team's investigation report.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:35.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:36.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:43.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you won't be dead for \Nanother five minutes or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:46.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's five minutes of hellish suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:48.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:54.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to end your \Nsuffering with this gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:58.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to say yes, you should \Ndo it while you can still talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:01.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:06.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:15.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,This is more than you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:25.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Quit shooting dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:30.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:36.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What you say is probably correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:39.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the normal way to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:45.01,sign_6715_64__Written_by_Asag,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(310,1)}Written by\NAsagiri Kafka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:45.01,sign_6715_65__Manga_by_Sango_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(310,1)}Manga by Sango \NHarukawa \Nin Young Ace
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:13.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:18.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is coming through, \Nand it's three times as cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:22.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Must have been rough, huh? Randou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,That was brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:26.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:29.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to guess why we were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The rumor is spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:36.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,If a Mori supporter like you were \Nto die in a black explosion,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:40.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,people would take the anger \Nof the former boss more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:45.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,One of the GSS soldiers \Nhe tore up on the way here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:49.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,had these instructions for \Nfaking a black explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,What's a "black explosion"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:55.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, you can get a black-ish flame
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:58.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,using a sodium lamp flame reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:03.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the case, it's just a cheap trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,So let me get this straight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:15.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,The GSS people attacked this guy, \Npretending to be Arahabaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:18.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,in order to get the Port Mafia to turn on itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,The current GSS president \Nis a cold-hearted man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:27.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it that he has close ties to The Guild,\Na North American secret organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:32.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about Arahabaki as you \Nsaw it in Suribachi City.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:38.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only lead we have on the \Nresurrection of the former president.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:41.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I remember it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,How could I ever forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I was the only survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:51.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,My subordinates all burned to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:55.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,They were engulfed by that black flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,It was no doubt that god of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:00.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:03.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:08.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,It happened close to the \Ncenter of Suribachi City.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:10.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Port Mafia,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:15.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,were on our way to battle the Sheep boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:22.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,There, out of the blue, we were all \Nblown away by a black explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,A sudden blastwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:38.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,All I could do was protect \Nmyself with my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Black flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Crumbling earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:45.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,It was hell itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:49.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,And in the middle, there it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't the former boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:09:01.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,No... It wasn't even human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,A beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:12.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,A beast of black flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:18.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Even its eyes were like \Nthe flames of purgatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:23.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Everything in sight was shimmering \Nin the extreme heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,except the Yokohama sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:29.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Just the sea, in the distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:32.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,basking gently in the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,That alone is vivid in my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,That moment, I heard the voice of the beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:45.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,It was a voice utterly devoid of emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:49.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,It terrified me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:57.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,You two wanted to prove that the former boss was not resurrected by Arahabaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:10:01.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,and it was a hoax put together\N by enemy gifted, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:05.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That was interesting indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:10.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, the mystery is solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:17.01,sign_14722_128_Episode_27,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 27
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:17.01,sign_14722_129_The_God_of_Fire,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The God of Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:24.77,sign_14822_131_A_derelict_at_th,Text,0000,0000,0000,,A derelict at the\N edge of town
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:24.93,sign_14846_132_Chuuya_and_Dazai,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya and Dazai \Ncollide violently
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:24.93,sign_14867_133_Tell_me_who_s__b,Text,0000,0000,0000,,"Tell me who's \Nbehind it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:24.93,sign_14906_134_No_way_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,"No way!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.93,sign_14927_135_Chuuya_quickly__,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya quickly \Ncloses in on Dazai
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.93,sign_14949_136_He_unleashes__a_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,He unleashes \Na powerful \Ndownward kick
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:30.94,sign_14990_137_Dazai_kicks_the_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai kicks the ground beneath\N him, leaping into the air \Naway from Chuuya
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:30.94,sign_15020_138_As_he_descends__,Text,0000,0000,0000,,As he descends, he swings \Ndown with the club in his hands
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.94,sign_15064_139__Hup__,Text,0000,0000,0000,,"Hup!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.94,sign_15077_140_Chuuya_blocks__w,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya blocks \Nwith both hands
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.94,sign_15092_141__Agh__,Text,0000,0000,0000,,"Agh!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:41.87,sign_15134_142_Dazai_lands_on_t,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai lands on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:41.87,sign_15147_143_Immediately__Chu,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately, Chuuya delivers \Na storm of punches
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:41.87,sign_15203_144__You_don_t__get_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,"You don't \Nget it,\N do you?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:41.87,sign_15248_145__No___I_do_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,"No, \NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:41.87,sign_15308_146_Unlike_a_certain,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike a certain \Ngrade-school \Nkid I happen\N to know!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.87,sign_15341_147_Dazai__takes__a_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai \Ntakes\N a step \Nback
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:47.00,sign_15395_148_Chuuya_hammers__,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya hammers \Nhim relentlessly \Nwith his fists
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:47.00,sign_15425_149__Come_on__come_o,Text,0000,0000,0000,,"Come on, come on!\N You're never going to \Nwin if you're always\N on the defensive!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.79,sign_15551_151_The_club_emits_a,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The club emits a\Ndestruction beam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Remember our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:07.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The loser has to obey one order \Nfrom the winner, like a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:11.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what should I have you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:14.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I was so sure I could win, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:17.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The strength of your ability is your downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:21.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's so strong that you never learn \Nto be cunning or to think tactically,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:24.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,whether it's video games or riddles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Riddles?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:29.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember ever doing \Nriddles, let alone losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:34.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's have a contest to see who \Ncan catch the perpetrator first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:38.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,If you win, we can call off the bet we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:42.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But if I win, you're my dog for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:46.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,You're on! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm neither cunning or tactical?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:52.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I ever show {\i1}you {\i0}\Nwhat I have up my sleeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:56.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Does the fact you always have your \Nfists closed and engage with your opponents
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:12:00.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,using just your kicks have something to \Ndo with what you have up your sleeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:03.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,How I fight is none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:04.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:07.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,So you're being lazy on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:12.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why are you looking for \Nthe god of fire, Arahabaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:14.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What got you interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:17.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0} so insistent on dying young?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:22.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The blue bracelets they're wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,They're members of the Sheep, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:34.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:37.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Does this seem like a good \Ntime for them to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:40.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nakahara Chuuya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Boss's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, mental?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:48.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We were looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:57.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Akira and Shougo were \Nabducted by the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:13:01.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to their base \Nand give them some pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:03.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Like we always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Dealing with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:11.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, dealing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:13.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:16.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell me what you \Nlearned about Arahabaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:19.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Have you discovered anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Is he interested in joining?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:24.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:27.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but would you mind \Nanswering his question?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:32.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Based on our investigation, \Nrumors about people seeing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:42.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,the previous boss or the black flame \Nhave exploded in the past week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What's the oldest confirmable rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:47.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Probably eight years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:51.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The giant explosion that created \NSuribachi City at the end of the conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:55.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Arahabaki didn't cause\Nany damage prior to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:57.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:01.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Is this kid really a newcomer to the Sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:05.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, let's come up \Nwith a plan to get our guys back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:07.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They were abducted from the \Nfactory road past the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:10.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on. You went past the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:13.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,You went to steal booze again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,So close to the Port Mafia base?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,It's right in the middle of the conflict!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,It's like asking to be abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:24.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're upholding our defensive policy, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:27.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this is a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:31.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Lay your hands on the Sheep and\N we hit back a hundred times harder. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:34.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it what you always say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:37.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That anyone who has the means others don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:39.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,they ought to fulfill that responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:43.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Fulfill your responsibility as someone \Nwho has an ability. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:48.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You two sure are interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:52.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one with the strongest power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:55.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,and he acts like a sheep \Nin the eyes of wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:59.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that leading an organization
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:01.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,is a lot harder than you'd imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:06.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take him with you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:09.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He's busy carrying out the\N Port Mafia's orders right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:10.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Chuuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're with the Port Mafia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:21.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:24.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything. Just don't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:25.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:30.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask Mori-san to release \Nthe hostages, so spare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:33.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you to contact him? Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:35.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:36.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:42.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We're making good progress \Non the work you ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding that, I want to ask for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:49.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Could you release the Sheep hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately. Unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The guards are contacting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:04.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,They've all been released?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:08.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Are we done here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:11.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:13.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We have work to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:14.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:17.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya doesn't do work for the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:17.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:19.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You have no more hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Chuuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:25.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:29.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. You guys go without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:33.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Arahabaki comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:38.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I made a bet with him \Nthat I'd find it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:41.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting for you \Nto beat down the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:43.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Lay off him already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:49.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He has the ability to choose for \Nhimself how to use his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:53.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Even a kid could figure out that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:55.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to discuss here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:59.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are the rumors actually true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:03.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That you betrayed the Sheep \Nand joined the Port Mafia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:05.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,The Port Mafia has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:08.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,This is my own problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare forget, Chuuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:15.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You had no family or relatives\N when the Sheep accepted you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:18.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:36.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:42.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine how happy that brat's \Ngoing to be when he finds out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:48.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,he's getting such a grand party in \Nhonor of his new-found freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:51.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:56.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,you said you found out \Nwho's behind Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:02.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you lie to torment Chuuya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Both, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:10.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I said what I did in front of him \Nso he'd take on the bet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:13.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but it's also true that \NI know who's behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:14.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:19.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You, Randou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:27.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You impersonated the former boss \Nand spread rumors about Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:29.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anything to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:32.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,What's your reasoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You've made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:38.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,A very basic mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,And what mistake is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:43.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:47.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You said this:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:51.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,When you saw Arahabaki \Nand the black flames...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:54.64,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Just the sea, in the distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:58.37,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,basking gently in the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:00.22,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,That alone is vivid in my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I did say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:08.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:11.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:13.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want \Nme to spoil it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It happened close to the \Ncenter of Suribachi City,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:22.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,and Suribachi City is a \Nhemispherical basin valley
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:25.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,that was carved out by the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:29.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:30.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:34.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you would have seen the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:37.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,If you were inside a giant depression \Nroughly two kilometers wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:41.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,the sea would never be within sight, \Nno matter how tall you stood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:44.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Why, then, did you say you saw the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:49.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You described Arahabaki with \Npersuasiveness that was almost truthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:51.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,So how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:56.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you did indeed see the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you made that mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:04.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You could only have seen the sea from \NSuribachi City before it was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:10.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Before the giant explosion eight years ago,\N at the end of the conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:15.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,You had a bet with Chuuya-kun, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:18.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Have you won that bet, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:21.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,You've beat him to the man behind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:40.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,And now I've won the bet \Nwith the suicidal maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:43.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,It was your doing, Randou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:46.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't fooling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:50.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I knew all along that you were lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:54.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:57.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:01.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I made \Nthe announcement first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:06.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I was just in the middle of explaining \Nthe method behind the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:09.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of? So you weren't done?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Then I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:15.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you've won, but I'll \Nlet you explain how you deduced it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:18.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,How did you deduce that\N Randou-san was behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:20.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,What is there to deduce?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:23.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone could have figured \Nit out from what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:29.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Every eyewitness so far has \Nsaid they saw the former boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:33.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,but this guy said he saw Arahabaki itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:39.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,There is no such thing as gods, \Nso you decided I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:42.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,The opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:48.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,It's because gods do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:52.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:56.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,You know that Arahabaki exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:57.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:21:59.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:01.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Eight years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:06.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you could have given\N such a precise account otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.17,0:22:14.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya-kun. Do you know \Nwhere Arahabaki is right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:17.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:19.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You should tell him if you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:27.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Randou-san's going to be executed for \Nputting the Port Mafia in danger, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:32.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, why the hell does everyone \Nwant to meet that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:36.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have the power \Nto revive the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:40.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't even have a \Npersonality or a mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.45,0:22:42.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as a typhoon or earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:45.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't need a personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.62,0:22:48.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Great destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:52.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Scorching the earth, staining the skies,\N rumbling the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.08,0:22:54.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,An unfathomable {\i1}thing{\i0} from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:22:58.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,That power is enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:03.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Chuuya-kun, where is this \Nthing beyond human comprehension,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.74,0:23:06.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,this thing that burned me alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:20.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you if you really want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:24.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Arahabaki is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:29.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:31.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:39.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I had a hunch that you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:40.00,sign_31816_385_Episode_27,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 28
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:40.00,sign_31816_386_The_God_of_Fire,Text,0000,0000,0000,,A Diamond is Only a Diamond
